{
  "stem": "10818.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But they, I guess, told my-- you know, secondhand told my parents that here was an opportunity.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "If you are courageous enough to let your daughter go by herself, in order to save her, then here's an opportunity where she can go to a school and live a relatively normal life and, and so on.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And also my parents weren't afraid of an English boarding school.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "One of my aunts had gone to one.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And so they felt that this was a, you know, all in all, a kind, the kind of experience which, under normal circumstances, I might have had a couple of years later, just to be in an English boarding school, just to learn English or something like that.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Of course, it's a different kind of an experience.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But that's how I was picked.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I-- you know, it seemed-- it was almost random.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I find myself in England, fortunately with my father not too far away, and suddenly learning everything in English.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And fortunately, as I said also, I had had enough English so that, you know, by the time I got a little acclimatized, I, I did very well in England and, and made good friends.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the question was, should I take what was then called School Certificate.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think it's now called A Levels.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't-- I forget what it's called.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it's, it's sort of an entrance exam into the universities.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, and the, the big question was, should we stay there until I was finished with, with it, for which I'd been preparing all year?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Or should we leave?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we were strongly advised, correctly, that we should go when it was our turn to go.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
